<LegalPage
  title="Cookies Policy"
  lastUpdated="12 October 2025"
  description="How cookies are (and aren't) used on the Diorama Consulting website."
>
  <section data-reveal>
    <p>This website currently does not set non-essential cookies for public visitors. We do not run analytics, advertising, or embedded media that place cookies.</p>
    <p>Strictly necessary cookies may be set only for administrative/log-in areas and are not used for general visitors. Under UK law, strictly necessary cookies do not require consent.</p>
  </section>

  <section data-reveal>
    <p>If we add analytics, embedded media (e.g., YouTube, Substack, Calendly), or other services that set non-essential cookies, we will:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Update this page with full details, and</li>
      <li>Display a cookie banner to obtain your consent before such cookies are set.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section data-reveal>
    <p>If you have questions, <a href="/contact">contact DioramaConsulting</a>.</p>
  </section>
</LegalPage>
